com.datastax.oss.driver.api.core.session

Class ProgrammaticArguments

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.datastax.oss.driver.api.core.session.ProgrammaticArguments

  • public class ProgrammaticArguments
extends Object
    The arguments that can be set programmatically when building a session.

    This is mostly for internal use, you only need to deal with this directly if you write custom SessionBuilder subclasses.
